1
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:42,440
Plan.

2
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:08,920
My son died tragically

3
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:11,880
because of your poor management.

4
00:01:12,320 --> 00:01:14,680
If I can't avenge my son,

5
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:17,480
you'll all be buried with him.

6
00:01:17,960 --> 00:01:19,240
Spare me, mother-in-law.

7
00:01:19,240 --> 00:01:21,300
There is something fishy about this.

8
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:29,440
Grandson.

9
00:01:30,039 --> 00:01:31,360
You're weak.

10
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:33,479
Don't kneel with them.

11
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,280
Thank you,

12
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:35,800
Grandma.

13
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:40,479
Now that

14
00:01:40,800 --> 00:01:42,039
your father is gone,

15
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:44,400
you must recover

16
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:47,479
to carry on the Tu family line

17
00:01:47,759 --> 00:01:50,280
and have many children.

18
00:01:51,039 --> 00:01:52,400
You should know

19
00:01:52,759 --> 00:01:55,280
that more sons mean more blessings.

20
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:57,280
Let me go.

21
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:58,479
Let go of me.

22
00:01:58,479 --> 00:01:58,920
Kneel.

23
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:02,440
You jinx.

24
00:02:03,240 --> 00:02:06,370
There really is an evil object in the Second Miss's room.

25
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:16,240
You wretch.

26
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:19,140
It was you who meddled with evil spirits,

27
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:21,970
and brought that thing here to kill my son.

28
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,079
Grandmother.

29
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:25,920
Who is your grandmother?

30
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:27,480
The Tu family

31
00:02:28,079 --> 00:02:29,940
has no place for a wretch like you.

32
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:37,079
It's because you insisted on keeping her here

33
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:39,880
that caused today's disaster.

34
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:41,770
Mother-in-law.

35
00:02:41,880 --> 00:02:43,079
Yunmeng doesn't seem like the type of child

36
00:02:43,079 --> 00:02:45,079
who would do such a thing.

37
00:02:45,320 --> 00:02:46,079
Perhaps...

38
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,810
Calm down, Mother-in-law.

39
00:02:48,880 --> 00:02:50,760
Everything has a cause and effect.

40
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:52,280
Everything is predestined.

41
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:54,480
Even if this matter is related to Yunmeng,

42
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:55,960
it wasn't what she wanted.

43
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:57,120
Fine.

44
00:02:57,760 --> 00:03:00,280
You're still pleading for this wicked creature.

45
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:02,280
Do you all want to be buried with her?

46
00:03:02,480 --> 00:03:04,040
I wouldn't dare.

47
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,280
Grandma,

48
00:03:05,600 --> 00:03:07,530
you need to think twice about this.

49
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,020
After all, Yunmeng

50
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:11,260
is also Father's flesh and blood.

51
00:03:12,720 --> 00:03:14,200
Silly child.

52
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:17,079
Your father was clearly killed by her.

53
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:19,220
And you are still deceived by her.

54
00:03:19,480 --> 00:03:22,079
Even your chronic illness,

55
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:23,160
I think,

56
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,600
is all caused by her.

57
00:03:25,440 --> 00:03:26,280
Just like her

58
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,960
bitch of a mother.

59
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:30,020
She should have died long ago.

60
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:31,960
My mother is not a bitch.

61
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:34,360
How dare you talk back!

62
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:39,120
You ungrateful wretch.

63
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:41,280
I will expel you from the Tu family today.

64
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:43,810
I won't let you talk about my mother like that.

65
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,160
What?

66
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:50,120
Still want to use dark magic on me?

67
00:03:50,920 --> 00:03:52,880
You ungrateful wretch.

68
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:56,560
Today I will expel you from the Tu family,

69
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:57,720
and use your head

70
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:59,210
as a sacrifice to my son.

71
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:01,960
I didn't kill my father! I didn't!

72
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:03,280
Still denying it?

73
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:05,490
Do you think I will let you go like this?

74
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:07,170
Whether you admit it or not,

75
00:04:07,440 --> 00:04:08,280
today

76
00:04:08,640 --> 00:04:09,960
you must die.

77
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:12,320
I will eliminate you

78
00:04:12,480 --> 00:04:14,680
and clean up the Tu family.

79
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:16,720
To avenge my son.

80
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:23,520
Old Madam.

81
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:25,080
Who are you?

82
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:26,760
To catch my cane

83
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:28,480
without even blinking.

84
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:29,880
Old lady.

85
00:04:30,280 --> 00:04:31,280
At your age,

86
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:32,680
you're quite strong.

87
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,480
Yunmeng.

88
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:36,880
Wake up.

89
00:04:39,159 --> 00:04:39,880
Old Madam.

90
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:42,130
She is your own granddaughter.

91
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,500
How can you be so cruel?

92
00:04:45,159 --> 00:04:46,000
Who

93
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:48,060
dares to act wildly in the Tu Mansion?

94
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:49,960
Reporting to Old Madam,

95
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:52,220
these two are from Yingtian Prefecture.

96
00:04:56,960 --> 00:04:59,159
Just a minor Yingtian Prefecture.

97
00:04:59,880 --> 00:05:01,200
I am punishing

98
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:02,760
the one who killed my son,

99
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:04,360
the main culprit.

100
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:06,730
No need for government interference.

101
00:05:06,960 --> 00:05:08,420
The truth is not yet clear.

102
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:10,320
How can you act so arbitrarily?

103
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:13,440
Look clearly.

104
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:15,720
This is the truth.

105
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:18,560
Aren't these just a bunch of handmade items?

106
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,480
What does that prove?

107
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:21,280
If I say it's her, then it's her.

108
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:24,200
If you are not convinced,

109
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:26,940
come talk to the dragon-head walking stick.

110
00:05:27,080 --> 00:05:29,080
You old lady are really unreasonable.

111
00:05:29,080 --> 00:05:30,840
Good thing you didn't go out to scam people.

112
00:05:30,840 --> 00:05:32,480
Otherwise, whoever ran into you would be unlucky.

113
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:32,880
You!

114
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:34,640
It's just a walking stick.

115
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:36,020
It's not a Gatling gun.

116
00:05:36,520 --> 00:05:37,650
Who are you scaring?

117
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:39,840
It was bestowed by the late Emperor.

118
00:05:39,840 --> 00:05:42,840
It grants the right to execute first and report later.

119
00:05:43,960 --> 00:05:45,420
I will spare you for today.

120
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:49,040
Now you know fear.

121
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:51,280
My ancestors

122
00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:54,040
once saved the late Emperor.

123
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:55,680
Therefore,

124
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:58,210
he bestowed this dragon-head walking stick.

125
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,160
Are you saying

126
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:02,320
back then at

127
00:06:02,320 --> 00:06:05,640
the person who led Emperor Taizong's donkey at Gaoliang River

128
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:07,000
was your grandfather?

129
00:06:08,320 --> 00:06:09,400
Of course not.

130
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:11,400
But the donkey pulling the cart

131
00:06:11,400 --> 00:06:13,130
was brought by my grandfather.

132
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,090
Bastard!

133
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:17,010
Why are you asking this?

134
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:19,280
I know you're anxious,

135
00:06:19,280 --> 00:06:20,680
but don't be anxious yet.

136
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:23,320
As long as I prove that mummy is not Lailan,

137
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:24,640
then the theory of corpse reanimation

138
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:25,500
will not stand.

139
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:28,080
What?

140
00:06:32,880 --> 00:06:34,200
You must be able to recognize

141
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:35,159
if the person on this

142
00:06:35,159 --> 00:06:36,400
is Lailan or not.

143
00:06:39,400 --> 00:06:40,600
I was right, wasn't I?

144
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:44,500
Someone placed the mummy at the scene

145
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:46,000
to fake a corpse mutation

146
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,330
and confuse the public.

147
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:49,080
I just don't understand.

148
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:51,440
Where on earth did this mummy come from?

149
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:54,520
Who exactly are you?

150
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:56,800
Can you let them go now, old lady?

151
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:04,000
In that painting,

152
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:05,800
it's clearly Lailan.

153
00:07:05,880 --> 00:07:07,120
You are obviously lying.

154
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:07,880
Look, look!

155
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:08,480
She blinked.

156
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,210
She blinked!

157
00:07:11,400 --> 00:07:12,600
I didn't blink.

158
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,800
You guys,

159
00:07:15,400 --> 00:07:16,930
tell me, is it Lailan or not?

160
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:24,370
Reporting to Madam,

161
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:25,880
this is Lailan.

162
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,040
Grandma,

163
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:30,760
this Liu Chuan

164
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:33,200
is the biggest spendthrift in Yingtian Prefecture.

165
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:35,400
He even angered his own father to death.

166
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:36,560
The words of such a person

167
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:38,280
are naturally untrustworthy.

168
00:07:38,280 --> 00:07:39,560
As for Yunmeng,

169
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:40,920
no wonder.

170
00:07:41,400 --> 00:07:43,800
He's speaking up for this wicked creature.

171
00:07:43,840 --> 00:07:45,170
It turns out they are all

172
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:48,680
the same kind of people who violate human ethics and filial piety.

173
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,240
Old lady,

174
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:50,900
don't make personal attacks.

175
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:55,600
But I have confirmed one thing.

176
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:56,680
You,

177
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,720
all of you,

178
00:07:58,159 --> 00:07:59,020
were all on that

179
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:00,600
Orient Express.

180
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:06,000
I don't know what nonsense you're talking about.

181
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,080
Don't forget,

182
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:08,560
this is the Tu Mansion.

183
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:11,000
What I have decided

184
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:12,760
is absolutely right.

185
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:15,200
Even if it's wrong,

186
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:18,000
you can only accept your bad luck.

187
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:21,530
You're being a rascal, aren't you?

188
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:26,480
Damn.

189
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:27,880
You can't play like this.

190
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,000
If I admit now

191
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:31,840
that Master Tu was killed by a corpse mutation,

192
00:08:31,840 --> 00:08:32,799
is it too late?

193
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:36,799
Liu Chuan,

194
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:38,799
sometimes being too smart

195
00:08:39,039 --> 00:08:40,600
will only harm yourself.

196
00:08:41,520 --> 00:08:44,179
I can't, for the sake of a maid's worthless life,

197
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:47,240
let down the ancestors of the Tu family.

198
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:49,320
This is her fate.

199
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:50,680
If I can't beat you,

200
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:51,960
can't I at least run away?
